    <title>Political Power and Mortality: Heterogeneous Effects of the U.S. Voting Rights Act</title>
    <updated>2025-11-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Atheendar Venkataramani, Rourke O'Brien, Elizabeth F. Bair &amp; Christopher A. Lowenstein</name>
